## Summary

The `HomeworkGrader` card allows users to view, answer, and get feedback on homework assignments. It includes features such as an overview of the assignment, a detailed view of each question, and a feedback section with the overall grade and score breakdown.

## Import

```
import { HomeworkGrader } from '../homework-grader';
```

## Usage as a Field

To use the `HomeworkGrader` card as a field within a consuming card or field:

```json
{
  "type": "card",
  "attributes": {
    "cardTitle": "Homework Assignment",
    "cardDescription": "Complete the homework and get feedback from the AI tutor."
  },
  "relationships": {
    "homework": {
      "data": {
        "type": "card",
        "id": "../homework-grader"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Template Usage

To display the `HomeworkGrader` card within a template:

```hbs
<@fields.homework />
```

This will render the `HomeworkGrader` card in the consuming card or field.
